  "text": "It is important to understand the behavior of the solution u of problem (1.2), given by (2.24). Consequently, it becomes necessary to recall some of the main properties of the modified Bessel function of the second kind K ν (z), ν ∈ R; see [1, Chapter 9.6] for (i)-(iv) and [CITATION_1] Theorem 5] ",
